A man has been critically wounded following a shooting incident that occurred in Ontdekkers Park , Roodepoort on Friday.It is reported that the incident happened around 6 .26 am.On arrival, paramedics found a Swazi immigrant lying on the ground in the yard of a private house with multiple gunshot wounds. The Advanced Life Support paramedic and her team worked fervently to stabilise the man at the scene before he was transported to a provincial hospital for further treatment, according to Netcare&#8217;s Chris Botha.The cause of the shooting is still speculative and will form part of the South African Police (SAPS) investigation.-TNA Reporter